  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "**A digital safe with multiple keys, held by people you trust.**",
    "context": "**A digital safe with multiple keys, held by people you trust.**\n\nReMemory protects your files and divides the key among people you choose. You decide how many must come together to open it. Each person gets a self-contained recovery tool that works offline, in any browser.*\n\n<sub>* [Time-locked](#time-delayed-recovery-experimental) archives need a brief internet connection at recovery time.</sub>",
    "cynefinDomain": "complex"
  },
